Invocation Name: our parish
des:
Our lady and all saints is a catholic parish located in Basildon, Essex, United Kingdom. We have developed Alexa skill to help all the people who visit the following churches below under this parish to know about the parish, mass timings and the contact details.

St Basil The Great
Luncies Road
Basildon
Essex
SS14 1SD


St Therese Of Lisieux
Florence Way
Langdon Hills
Essex
SS16 6AJ


The Most Holy Trinity
Wickhay
Basildon
Essex
SS15 5AD

you can say "Alexa ask Our Parish" then you ask any of the following questions

"tell me about our lady and all saints",
"tell me about Our parish"
"when is the mass at Holy trinity church",
"contact parish",
"Where is the parish",
"say a prayer"
"exit"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
